<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="pub-section pub-section-alt">
    <h2 class="pub-section-title pub-fade-up">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="pub-faq-list pub-fade-up">
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">How long is the free trial?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">14 days with full access to all features in your selected plan. No credit card required to start. At the end of the trial, choose a plan or export your data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">What counts as a "machine"?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">Any production asset that appears on your Gantt schedule &mdash; SLS printers, CNC mills, depowder stations, wire EDM machines, finishing stations, etc. QC and inspection stations do not count toward the limit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">Can I switch plans later?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">Yes. Upgrade or downgrade anytime. When upgrading, you get immediate access to new features. When downgrading, changes take effect at the end of your current billing cycle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">Do you offer annual billing?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">Yes. Annual billing saves 20% compared to monthly pricing. Contact us for a custom quote on the Enterprise tier.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">Is my data secure?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">All data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.2+) and at rest. Your production data is isolated per tenant &mdash; no other customer can access it. Enterprise plans offer ITAR-compliant hosting and on-premise deployment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">What kind of support is included?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">All plans include email support from engineers who understand additive manufacturing. Professional plans get priority response times. Enterprise plans get a dedicated support engineer and phone support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-faq-item">
            <h3 class="pub-faq-question">Can I import existing data?</h3>
            <p class="pub-faq-answer">Yes. Vectrik supports CSV import for parts, work orders, and machine data so you can get up and running quickly. API access is available on Professional and Enterprise plans for ongoing integration with your existing ERP, CAM, and other systems.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Bottom CTA -->
<section class="pub-cta-banner">
    <h2 class="pub-gradient-text">Start your free trial today</h2>
    <p>14 days free. No credit card required. Full access to all features in your selected plan.</p>
    <a href="/demo" class="pub-btn pub-btn-primary pub-btn-lg">Get Started</a>
</section>
